snippet.title: Welcome to Gamecube World! ("Peach's Castle" Tech Demo)
snippet.description:
A tech demo produced by Nintendo as part of the 5-22-2001 GameCube SDK, to show off the capabilities of the console to developers. This video consists of a full loop of  the "AUTO DEMO" mode,  rendered in 1080p in the Dolphin emulator, with the original audio.

More Info: https://www.unseen64.net/2009/03/01/peachs-castle-gamecube-tech-demo/

Border Photo: https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Evan-Amos
